Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on V2X communication, which is a type of networking architecture. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses resource allocation and interference mitigation techniques, which are related to information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper evaluates the system-level performance of LTE V2X network, which is related to systems and control. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper may touch upon security issues related to V2X communication. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may discuss the use of multimedia in V2X communication.
